-- Greece's NBG confirms 2.5 bln euro share issue in May
-- 
-- Wed Apr 16, 2014 01:18PM EDT
-- None



ATHENS, April 16 (Reuters) - Greece's largest lender National Bank (NBG) <NBGr.AT> confirmed on Wednesday it will go ahead with an equity offering of up to 2.5 billion euros ($3.45 billion) to plug a capital gap revealed last month by a stress test.

